{
  "stem": "18813.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 409.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You were with Schindler.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was during the war that transport came over-- beautiful guys, beautiful, young fellows.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were coming-- when they opened the doors, it was just like sardines, you know, falling out-- that frozen.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because in Poland, the winters-- you know, in Auschwitz, when they were-- make Appell and the snow was coming to me, you know, it was reminding me the tree was shaking, back and forth, because we were holding each other to be warm.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the same dress-- I was going on that wooden bed-- with the bed with the bench-- bunks what we had.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[SIGHS] And, and the steam was coming out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And by the time the steam stopped a little bit, we had to go out because they were counting us again at night, counting without stopping.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because we were not working.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Auschwitz, we never worked one day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were three and a half weeks, I think, in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I said, we were lucky we survived, very lucky, especially Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like my girlfriend was standing next to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she said, Esther, what smells like that?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were naked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just going in, and Mengele with the stick-- Mengele, he was in charge of Auschwitz-- with a stick, 1, 2, 3.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she looks at me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she said, ah, I think woman with big breasts going on the-- there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She said, I think if you have small breasts, you're no good.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Do you smell something? she said to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, we're going in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that's it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, let's go together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were-- we were hundred percent sure we're going into the fire.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we were lucky.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
